  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    State
    public class Position
extends Point
    Represent a position in 2D space (for example of a org.greenblitz.example.robot) that consists of x, y, and angle (heading, the direction the object faces)

    • Field Detail

      • angle

        protected double angle
        The angle of this position. This representation is like in math: 1. In radians 2. Between -PI and PI 3. 0 radians = facing positive y (in FRC coords) 4. Goes counter clockwise
